snippet.title: Suicide Squad: Kill the Justice League - Official Season 2 'Meet Mrs. Freeze' Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Suicide Squad: Kill the Justice League is a third-person action-adventure game developed by Rocksteady. Season 2 has arrived to the game bringing a multiversal cold front to Metropolis alongside Mrs. Freeze and her plans to save the Flash needing to ice Brainiac in the process. Season 2's Free Content Update is available now for PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox Series X|S, and PC.
